title: FREE YuGiOh Tournaments every Saturday at 2pm
desc: FREE YuGiOh tournaments every Saturday at 2pm. The Winner on Saturday will receive 15 Astral Packs and 2nd Place on Saturday will receive 5 Astral Packs.
